{"tid":1515583,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請立即使用VPN以防緊急法封殺連登","createTime":"2019-08-29T08:25:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T11:24:31.000Z","uid":66895,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c615c06f79e6b7a58ecbafe56be41e47d07052d8","tid":1515583,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:25:20.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇流言終結者巴打講解咩係vpn<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1502172/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1502172/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n緊急法賦予政府無限權力，如果林鄭真係推行緊急法，好大機會第一件事就係封殺連登同telegram。但係連登server係外國，而telegram又係外國公司，冇可能迫令兩個平台停止運作，所以好大機會只係好似大陸咁用防火牆，令牆內嘅香港人冇得上呢個網站。<br />\n<br />\n就算我哋想攬炒，都要保持同其他人嘅聯絡。而如果唔用連登轉其他平台，我哋未必知道安唔安全，會唔會比admin出賣，所以建議大家到時翻牆用連登。<br />\n<br />\n除咗到時可以翻牆用連登之外，VPN另一個好處係可以保護到自己嘅身份，如果唔係睇你ip就知你係邊。<br />\n<br />\n建議大家即刻下載付費嘅VPN。大家記住，千祈唔好用免費嘅VPN，因為好多都係大陸提供。免費嘅嘢永遠都係最貴。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇依個網，比較唔同嘅VPN。好多都好平，廿幾蚊一個月，download落黎都好易。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/vpn/best-vpn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techradar.com%2Fvpn%2Fbest-vpn&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=ebb5358a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techradar.com/vpn/best-vpn</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔太熟科技野，希望多啲experts可以講下cyber security。"},{"pid":"e9ad7c537054d70ae8bd0919987a7beabcd884f4","tid":1515583,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8e0275283215c834828fca4f9c25ec3b9e6e66b","tid":1515583,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d946550dc032a4a02734b9f2985fcb40afa4ac","tid":1515583,"uid":776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:27:28.000Z","ms